{"tid":1081210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李寶安決定TVB全力進軍大灣區市場　除咗拍綜藝仲想起電視城！","createTime":"2019-03-28T06:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T03:36:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"820472e722a5a175ecc9e8cb4e05f811a054c655","tid":1081210,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2598690/org/d1bedc4a96d4c9cb783b4f2e3e73d701.jpg/9yd-AUrKIaVyZsTcg-D93LAqIYQV36ps7TH13-0x9d8?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2598690%2Forg%2Fd1bedc4a96d4c9cb783b4f2e3e73d701.jpg%2F9yd-AUrKIaVyZsTcg-D93LAqIYQV36ps7TH13-0x9d8%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=993f4c8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTVB行政總裁李寶安昨日在接受傳媒訪問時表示，公司會向著OTT業務、大台網及內地業務這三個目標發展，並找尋增長動力，期望今年可在內地推出綜藝節目，開拓收入來源，在大灣區覓地建廠，爭取由以往收費提供節目予內地電視台轉播，改為無需收費但可播放自家廣告。<br />\n<br />\n講到尾，向內地發展絕對是TVB的重要任務，原因當然是賺錢，而大灣區絕對是項目的核心地帶，而無綫希望可以進軍大灣區的免費電視頻道，首要的條件當然是製作配合大灣區的節目。<br />\n<br />\nTVB的劇集一直也有與內地合拍，所以今次重點並不是放在劇集身上，而是綜藝節目。根據李寶安在接受傳媒訪問時的說法，會跟內地網上平合作拍攝綜藝節目，打算將以往較成功的作品為先鋒，例如在《香港小姐》、《國際中華小姐》等選美節目中添加中國色彩，也不排除再增添選美節目，不過目前未有定案。其實好簡單，直接搞一個《大灣區小姐競選》，又可以攻打大灣區地方，又有綽頭，一定得！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2598665/org/64eaeb3ddfa3e1d34bfe0f293a10fe96.jpg/BZ8pM8ipXEUvNcotoxmLq6WzQvfAZ1uwhXk1JKN5NSQ?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2598665%2Forg%2F64eaeb3ddfa3e1d34bfe0f293a10fe96.jpg%2FBZ8pM8ipXEUvNcotoxmLq6WzQvfAZ1uwhXk1JKN5NSQ%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=757d5e6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了選美節目，其實TVB也有一些綜藝節目適合加入中國元素，首先當然要選出皇牌綜藝，例如《Do姐去Shopping》又或是《森美旅行團》，至於如何加入中國元素？好簡單，請個客席嘉賓！早前《Do姐再Shopping》也是Do姐農夫為固定主持，再加一個TVB藝員作客席嘉賓，今次只要邀請內地人氣高的藝人，輕易地加入中國元素，又可以靠他的人氣爭取內地觀眾收看，又贏一仗！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/310732/%E6%9D%8E%E5%AF%B6%E5%AE%89%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9Atvb%E5%85%A8%E5%8A%9B%E9%80%B2%E8%BB%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E9%99%A4%E5%92%97%E6%8B%8D%E7%B6%9C%E8%97%9D%E4%BB%B2%E6%83%B3%E8%B5%B7%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%9F%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F310732%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259Atvb%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%2580%25B2%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%2592%2597%25E6%258B%258D%25E7%25B6%259C%25E8%2597%259D%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E6%2583%25B3%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%259F%258E&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AMWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=1c69b4de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/310732/%E6%9D%8E%E5%AF%B6%E5%AE%89%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9Atvb%E5%85%A8%E5%8A%9B%E9%80%B2%E8%BB%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E9%99%A4%E5%92%97%E6%8B%8D%E7%B6%9C%E8%97%9D%E4%BB%B2%E6%83%B3%E8%B5%B7%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%9F%8E</a>"},{"pid":"b75fa8683a14b8bc85deb2872afd4a0538171157","tid":1081210,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T06:56:09.000Z","msg":"拍紅色娘子軍呀"},{"pid":"8c375d76e3ed972eea95b7831ccbaf84d3541ce3","tid":1081210,"uid":36040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T06:56:58.000Z","msg":"政治任務"},{"pid":"7948963962f8a340e6153699b6c915bf86929f98","tid":1081210,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"咪即係再加強自我審查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2341ff1ccdb03a5bd46bd2074589a4fdbed50232","tid":1081210,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T07:02:15.000Z","msg":"無綫劇習"},{"pid":"e8b031c013851fa0cd1cda8166f5ccb821e5e584","tid":1081210,"uid":92697,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T07:03:43.000Z","msg":"外資就急急腳走<br